      "y": 810,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "BEFORE (formula)                    AFTER (rubric)                         CHANGE\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nthesis_beta (0.0-1.0)           →   Thesis Alignment (5 levels)            Same concept, categorical\nconvexity (capped at 20x)      →   Payoff Shape (5 levels)                Same concept, categorical\ntime_cost (annualized %)       →   Timing Forgiveness (4 levels)          Reframed: cost → robustness\nalready_priced_in (yes/no)      →   Edge (4 levels)                        Upgraded: binary → graded\nScore each → pick highest       →   Assess rubric → compare head-to-head   Structured judgment\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nUNCHANGED:\n• Hard gates (contradiction, liquidity, time mismatch)\n• Connection floor (retry if alignment is Partial/Tangential)\n• Cross-check (always compare across instrument classes)\n• Stress-test (construct case against the winner)\n• Binary check (prediction markets set the ceiling)\n• Output format (The Take + The Card)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "baseline": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#495057"
    },


